{
  "stem": "8842.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, they also lived in Kalvarija.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we used to spend sometime summers there, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We loved it very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of the summers, my parents used to take us to vacations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she used to-- they used to [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SIGHS] take a house-- not actually a house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, like, in a farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Farms used to have special little home-- little apartments for vacations--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--away really in the country, sometimes-- a real farm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother used to rent a little place like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all used to spend the two months of our vacations in the woods there free, running around like wild little kids.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father used to come to us weekends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those were the most beautiful, beautiful summers we always had together-- fresh milk, eggs, running around the farms, and watching how they milk the cows, and running on the horses and wild in the woods.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was my most beautiful feeling-- going in the woods and picking-- my mother used to ask us to pick up some strawberries and-- blueberries we used to pick in the woods those days.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Bring the full baskets full to make all kind of goodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1941, the summer that I was sent from school with very gifted children together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was under the Russians already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians came, where-- they, they took over Lithuania--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Summer, we were in a camp of children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all either-- were good dancers or singing or playing all kind of instruments.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a special music camp, they used to call it, away from the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were all there having the time of our lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's the-- that is the funniest thing that I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
